Recycleview helps to deal with a large number of data items. Recycleview provides the user with the
flexibility to scroll down or scroll-up the data displayed in the kivy application.

You can also select multiple data items at once.
Recycleview is memory efficient as compared to Listview.





To use RecycleView you have to first import it.

[from kivy.uix.recycleview import RecycleView]